data.text:
I am pleased to announce my new position as Studio Manager at Orange Video! Orange Video is a full service video production company based out of Tallahassee, Florida. I have worked with Orange Video previously as a Production Assistant last December for a three day production. I then got asked to step into the part-time role of Studio Manager at the beginning of April. As a Studio Manager I help with the pre-production and post production process and assist with business running smoothly. I am so grateful for this opportunity and I am excited to learn more about the production process!

The amount of applicants LinkedIn shows have applied is not true. I repeat. The amount of applicants LinkedIn shows have applied is *not true*. My team at nextOPP Search is currently recruiting for a number companies, from inside their ATS (Greenhouse, Ashby, Workable, Lever, Recruitee, and more) and I am baffled by the misinformation. A job I posted 3 days ago via the company ATS shows 100+ applicants on the LinkedIn posting. In the ATS? 36. So please don't be put off by the competition. It's fake news! Apply. You've got this.
